==Personnel==
* Written and composed by [[Michael Jackson]], [[Paul Anka]]
* Arrangements by Michael Jackson, John McClain, Franck van der Heijden and [[Timbaland]]
* Produced by Michael Jackson, John McClain, [[Giorgio Tuinfort]], Timbaland, [[Jerome "J-Roc" Harmon|J-Roc]] and [[Justin Timberlake]]
* Mixed by [[Dave Pensado]]
* Featured and additional background vocals by Justin Timberlake
* Keyboard by Paul Anka
* Horns by [[Benjamin Wright (composer)|The Regiment Horns]]
* Percussion by Terry Santiel
* Guitars by  Elliott Ives and Mike Scott
* Bass by  Mike Scott

