==Cover versions==
* American pop music singer [[Johnny Mathis]] released this song for his 1984 album ''[[A Special Part of Me]]'' with new lyrics by Anka and [[Kathleen Wakefield]], which was the song's first released version.<ref name=history />
* German jazz guitarists Gismo Graf Trio covered this song in their 2014 album ''Modus Vivendi''.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.de/Modus-Vivendi-Gismo-Graf-Trio/dp/B00HX67M14/ | title=Modus Vivendi: Amazon.de: Musik | publisher=Amazon.de | work=amazon.de | date=17 Jan 2014 | accessdate=11 May 2014}}</ref>

